;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEyMTNfMjY1/MDAxNjcwOTIyMTU3MTY0.eXZinyFEtx8M5dNcs0OPE24r4M9y-vacF5EhVRnWv8Ig.TxDelvEAiZ5fLOUiUaAgNceJEC5x7UI3pKEG2T8_QBYg.PNG.cookthedesign/1.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0ca41670-30c7-4358-b359-51d3d68c10a4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4be4bbcc-c6eb-440e-9531-a4cbb67a407c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-953794fe-d7b7-4857-a95b-5a3adfe00892\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>절수의 의미</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6e793f55-5c42-4b65-aef6-c4c4cc27d603\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-32994690-64f2-4710-9023-ff9a9f08cf01\" style=\"color:#555555;\">절수란 종이가 출고될 때 절단해서 판매되는 사이즈를 말합니다. 국전지와 46전지로 나눠지고 A, B 사이즈가 그 절수안에 포함되게 됩니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ce53c55e-b91c-4e5c-8ca5-ec509aef781b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c7ca8dbd-4c51-49b2-82d5-b47a51d10e82\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b71531eb-316d-46fc-b77b-059e80089137\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-15a8839a-c8e7-433a-8994-4993ecc15db7\" style=\"color:#000000;\">46전지의 절수는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e327794d-104c-423f-8d1c-e3e6c862cce2\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7ce2f481-4440-41dd-8051-f600ec50085e\" style=\"color:#000000;\">788mm × 1091mm입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fcd9e598-364e-4845-b413-8e675998bd68\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9b28d43f-15de-401d-8a51-48cf96111913\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ab2fdda5-0f32-4e2d-b7d9-6d38c40fccbe\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-024abf77-5ac2-4c7b-bb0e-b45b6a240634\" style=\"color:#000000;\">국전지의 절수는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-69519609-1108-479e-a6c7-46e983c7f99e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4def97c1-79ec-41b8-9abf-bdb3179be392\" style=\"color:#000000;\">636mm × 939mm입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0aae0ab2-77f2-4fca-977f-efc585a7b23d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d2d72954-d339-4aba-8a84-797c597c65c7\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-53e98a41-088d-4d16-ad97-46625f6b8914\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-53e98a41-088d-4d16-ad97-46625f6b8914\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEyMTNfMjEg/MDAxNjcwOTIzNzE3NjI1.pdl3DvWtYCFOYQC6RLrruv7UmG7jd1y6rLpG5ct6IqQg.5YBepaxPrudAKxyyo6f5fsHy7cn-c2FFczGulgTofFYg.PNG.cookthedesign/30_%EC%82%AC%EC%9D%B4%ED%8A%B8%EC%84%A4%EB%AA%85_221112.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1184\", \"originalHeight\" : \"830\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEyMTNfMjEg/MDAxNjcwOTIzNzE3NjI1.pdl3DvWtYCFOYQC6RLrruv7UmG7jd1y6rLpG5ct6IqQg.5YBepaxPrudAKxyyo6f5fsHy7cn-c2FFczGulgTofFYg.PNG.cookthedesign/30_%EC%82%AC%EC%9D%B4%ED%8A%B8%EC%84%A4%EB%AA%85_221112.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a7116064-6059-4b27-af77-27032500cc9e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:488px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-a7116064-6059-4b27-af77-27032500cc9e\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEyMTNfMjc4/MDAxNjcwOTI0NjA1NDM5.FrpjT6y58DQZY8QxdFYUeQjPmuCexwgZOZWeR_PVhBwg.FFX6vXSFN4quT-TmjTy2YCdyIfYb2qrwZUX3g7H_UHAg.PNG.cookthedesign/30_%EC%82%AC%EC%9D%B4%ED%8A%B8%EC%84%A4%EB%AA%85_221112.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"488\", \"originalHeight\" : \"405\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEyMTNfMjc4/MDAxNjcwOTI0NjA1NDM5.FrpjT6y58DQZY8QxdFYUeQjPmuCexwgZOZWeR_PVhBwg.FFX6vXSFN4quT-TmjTy2YCdyIfYb2qrwZUX3g7H_UHAg.PNG.cookthedesign/30_%EC%82%AC%EC%9D%B4%ED%8A%B8%EC%84%A4%EB%AA%85_221112.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b2706218-9c83-405f-b650-a1fefc2da388\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-b2706218-9c83-405f-b650-a1fefc2da388\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEyMTNfMTc4/MDAxNjcwOTI0NjkzNTY2.nr7laOuHzRWh79isBVojHuy8Z9B235mWFG16nEMrqocg.L2q-x1KFQfUo1XCH_fwlYtUexL-6L6un0pXC5iMAEhgg.PNG.cookthedesign/30_%EC%82%AC%EC%9D%B4%ED%8A%B8%EC%84%A4%EB%AA%85_221112.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1555\", \"originalHeight\" : \"349\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEyMTNfMTc4/MDAxNjcwOTI0NjkzNTY2.nr7laOuHzRWh79isBVojHuy8Z9B235mWFG16nEMrqocg.L2q-x1KFQfUo1XCH_fwlYtUexL-6L6un0pXC5iMAEhgg.PNG.cookthedesign/30_%EC%82%AC%EC%9D%B4%ED%8A%B8%EC%84%A4%EB%AA%85_221112.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-08790f0a-c6b3-4ab2-b71f-eee291878c3d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-23cc3663-97fd-44b4-979d-35f3dfab4ba5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0bb20784-1146-46b6-ad42-bc25e22085fc\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7bf01726-d687-426d-8e11-976b81ed6159\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-16e7cb1d-6e19-450e-9691-2121a88fedc8\" style=\"color:#000000;\">위의 표가 보이시나요? 개발기획 팀장으로 있을 때 정리한 사이즈 조건표입니다. 저는 이미 여러번 말씀드렸듯이 인쇄관련 실무 기획팀장경력이 10년차 이상입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-966f3dca-e9c2-4cfb-b0cb-7c1e1640e12e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fd67b121-35f0-4334-86cb-13e2693d4c2e\" style=\"color:#000000;\">사이즈 정리만 3일동안 엑셀을 만들 만큼 상품에 따라 사이즈 변동이 심한 것이 인쇄분야입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a06285d2-f11f-443e-9f42-fe3250ec1bd9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0202de8e-6ed2-47bc-aa59-cecf13411c84\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8cb47db4-e8f2-4c95-bf32-cdd9a8494153\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bd5213ce-bee1-4a1b-b72d-8ce798b521c0\" style=\"color:#000000;\">고객 여러분은 A4만 알고 계서도 됩니다. 나머지는 인쇄소에서 알아서 사이즈를 정리해 드릴것입니다. 다만 사이즈에 따라 인쇄가 되거나 또는 가격이 많이 변경되는 부분도 있으니 주의하시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f092f1bc-f5c0-4af7-8bb9-cd40c25d1313\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6bfc88b1-b3a9-4824-99dc-2f53a5622c6a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-6bfc88b1-b3a9-4824-99dc-2f53a5622c6a\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEyMTNfMjc2/MDAxNjcwOTI0OTEzNTA5.TGhrC9BF3_QvXUFcnJZC9L6mwJlmnbgT_Z0kcOmIgrEg._iIUqoDzvhXL8pIKY8CUGlqo5CM8D0F5pVevms7GqTQg.PNG.cookthedesign/2.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"2364\", \"originalHeight\" : \"237\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEyMTNfMjc2/MDAxNjcwOTI0OTEzNTA5.TGhrC9BF3_QvXUFcnJZC9L6mwJlmnbgT_Z0kcOmIgrEg._iIUqoDzvhXL8pIKY8CUGlqo5CM8D0F5pVevms7GqTQg.PNG.cookthedesign/2.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0fb14416-5ee2-4bf4-abaa-97153f32bd26\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-03eedbe4-59bf-40a0-a469-ccf24d42eb4e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-b85829cf-0f0d-4010-ab76-fc855347af39\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>상품에 따른 기본사이즈</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-28ce1845-1c16-4298-b4fc-6fad463946af\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b19960b3-08ce-42e4-aece-1b11752d77d7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">보통 인쇄에서는 상품에 따른 기본사이즈가 존재합니다. 이 말은 명함의 사이즈는 90mm × 50mm, 이런 기본을 말합니다. 다음은 기본적인 상품의 제일 인기있는 사이즈를 나열했습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cb320e4d-0f01-4539-857a-e30579b37314\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-80e9ace8-6b08-4c95-ac56-5c875444850a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ee18bbab-104a-4d4e-9790-17e706f24176\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:572px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-